reviewText: This course was suitable to learn about the basic knowledge on International Business. And some of reading assignments were very interesting since they used actual examples and experiences. However there were some mistakes or issues on PP slides and Quizzes, which was a bit frustrating to me and made me think it unreliable. Overall, it was worth taking this lecture.
